## Performance Checklist

- [ ] **Virtualize large lists** (1000+ items)
- [ ] **Use React.memo** for expensive components
- [ ] **Memoize callbacks** with useCallback
- [ ] **Memoize computations** with useMemo
- [ ] **Debounce/throttle** expensive operations
- [ ] **Use requestAnimationFrame** for scroll/visual updates
- [ ] **Preload adjacent items** for smooth navigation
- [ ] **Clean up all subscriptions** in stop()
- [ ] **Clear all intervals/timeouts** in stop()
- [ ] **Abort async operations** when component unmounts
- [ ] **Filter failed items** to prevent rendering issues
- [ ] **Use ErrorBoundary** for user-facing components

---

## Memory Checklist

- [ ] **Clear all caches** in stop()
- [ ] **Remove all event listeners** in cleanup
- [ ] **Clear all intervals/timeouts** in cleanup
- [ ] **Abort all pending requests** in cleanup
- [ ] **Close all modals** in stop()
- [ ] **Clear all refs** (set to null)
- [ ] **Remove all state listeners** in cleanup
- [ ] **Reset all global state** in stop()

---

## Error Handling Checklist

- [ ] **Wrap async operations** in try-catch
- [ ] **Handle AbortError** separately (don't show error)
- [ ] **Show user-friendly error messages** via Toasts
- [ ] **Log errors** with Logger for debugging
- [ ] **Use ErrorBoundary** for components
- [ ] **Validate inputs early** before processing
- [ ] **Check array bounds** before access
- [ ] **Use optional chaining** for safe property access
- [ ] **Add safety checks** for undefined APIs

